<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><hymn_number>493</hymn_number>
<author>lǚ xiǎo mǐn</author>
<title>dà néng shǒu 迦南493</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 dà néng shǒu, dà néng shǒu, zǒng yǒu yī shuāng dà néng shǒu chān fú wǒ.
 miàn duì shì sú zǔ dǎng, miàn duì wàn jiā dēng huǒ, zǒng yǒu yī shuāng dà néng shǒu chān fú wǒ.
 cuī dòng wǒ de xuè yè, zàn měi gē shēng bù jué, zǒng yǒu yī shuāng dà néng shǒu chān fú wǒ.
 pān dēng mǎng mǎng qīng shān, zǒu guò xiǎo xiǎo yuàn luò, zǒng yǒu yī shuāng dà néng shǒu chān fú wǒ.</lyrics>
</song>